title: Romulus Miclea
text: Romulus Miclea (born 5 April 1980 in <a href="T%C3%A2rgu%20Mure%C8%99">Târgu Mureș</a>) is a <a href="Romania">Romania</a>n <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player who plays as a <a href="Midfielder%23Winger">right winger</a> for <a href="ASA%20T%C3%A2rgu%20Mure%C8%99%20%281962%29">ASA Târgu Mureș</a>.
